    public class SafeSortedMap<K,​V>
extends ConcurrentSkipListMap<K,​V>
    Implementation of a SortedMap extending ConcurrentSkipListMap to support null keys and null values.

    23.03

        public Map.Entry<K,​V> getEntry​(K oKey)
